data.value: Whenever customers book appointments with your business through the booking page, they are asked to key-in some details. For example, name, phone number, email and so forth. This information remains crucial for business owners to maintain a customer database and also for future perusal. But in case of returning customers, adding in the details over and over again could be a strain for your clients.
